metadata.title: High Resolution Seismic Reflection Data Beaufort and Chukchi Seas-Alaskan OCS USGS Open File Reports 82-33 & 81-34

creators.name: Atmospheric Administration (NOAA), National Environmental Satellite, Data
Information Service (NESDIS), National Geophysical Data Center (NGDC)

metadata.description:
Approximately 9,384-line km of single-channel high-
resolution Uniboom continuous seismic reflection profiles along
88 tracklines in the Beaufort and Chukchi Seas are now available
for purchase from the National Geophysical Data Center (NGDC).
The data were collected by the U.S. Geological Survey (USGS)
during two cruises of the R/V SAMUEL P. LEE in August 25 through
October 5, 1977, and August 22 through September 19, 1978.*
